The,Data,CRM,API,allows,developers,to,access,data,from,multiple,CRM,platforms,via,a,single,unified,interface,This,service,allows,users,to,retrieve,add,update,delete,and,sync,stored,data,Data,CRM,supports,more,than,platforms,including,Salesforce,Zoho,SugarCRM,Highrise,and,Insightly,It,also,provides,an,automated,migration,service,which,guarantees,error,free,data,transfer,and,uptime,for,the,user,s,current,CRM,during,the,transfer